===Pronunciation===
זכר / zâkâr / zaw-kawr'

===Etymology===
From זכר / zâkar {{HH|2142}}; 

===Noun===
'''זכר'''

# Properly remembered, that is, a [[male]] (of man or animals, as being the most noteworthy sex): -  X him, male, [[man]] ([[child]], -kind).

